{"tid":1987892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"YouTube自動刪除含有「共匪」嘅comment","createTime":"2020-04-24T19:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T02:46:32.000Z","uid":262677,"like":137,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"a6edd2535eb263935378cb9d5bf23d9d87cfda1a","tid":1987892,"uid":262677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T19:51:04.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪old news，不過是但啦<br />\n<br />\n事源早排小弟喺youtube度同個小粉紅舌戰，有幾個reply喺send完之後消失咗，之後我就懷疑係咪因為我用咗「共匪」字眼俾youtube刪reply<br />\n<br />\n為咗證實唔係其他人刪嘅，小弟自己upload咗條全黑片嚟測試，呢到我首先send咗個齋得「共匪」嘅comment，可以見到係send咗出去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v9MJecA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv9MJecA.png&h=975ee4a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後我再reply「共匪」，都成功send咗出去，仲可以love comment。但好快就出事，繼續㩒love comment會出現unknown error，其實個comment已經被del咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7kWMWjQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7kWMWjQ.png&h=5134b577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我嘗試再reply去初頭個comment到，但就彈comment failed to post嘅錯誤信息<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bAUCizz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbAUCizz.png&h=bb160637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我重新開過條片，可以見到嗰兩條齋得「共匪」嘅comment已經唔見咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gibk0OQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGibk0OQ.png&h=c2f96f1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知youtube做乜鳩要禁共匪呢個詞，但事實就係有「共匪」嘅comment會被youtube自動刪除，睇嚟好快喺youtube度打comment都要好似中國噉啲字要搵啲嘢隔開先出到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋呢啲事唔係最近先有，上年三月已經有人喺google support度講過<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.google.com/youtube/thread/2241279?hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fyoutube%2Fthread%2F2241279%3Fhl%3Den&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn0VeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=f5b42355\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/youtube/thread/2241279?hl=en</a><br />\n<br />\n如果懷疑我做假嘅可以自己去youtube試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d541c9b9cc0035ba1feed8e8d9b931e0b3014942","tid":1987892,"uid":123988,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:01:05.000Z","msg":"都好堅，舔共舔到雪雪聲"},{"pid":"852caef97fe7e64f148a92c7e725860753e3680d","tid":1987892,"uid":59976,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:02:24.000Z","msg":"be evil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712900638dfa12106b342a8086c4e6365925c142","tid":1987892,"uid":307967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:03:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c70394d171b6e44030e92feb28c4893236fd6c0d","tid":1987892,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"852caef97fe7e64f148a92c7e725860753e3680d","tid":1987892,"uid":59976,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:02:24.000Z","msg":"be evil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:03:53.000Z","msg":"don&rsquo;t be just<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0682ce3d6f147a7ff75ab0b9a7549899972306","tid":1987892,"uid":246023,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:04:41.000Z","msg":"youtube比人話奶共都唔係一日半日"},{"pid":"f3be08244e5ed6132d49bd30ce6a424538c11c52","tid":1987892,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T21:20:55.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"6d79577455d9499b19c5f90a0aaca18d80b9beb6","tid":1987892,"uid":89302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T21:22:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3765b72e69ed867e5b61b511a990b6462376cb01","tid":1987892,"uid":192754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T21:23:28.000Z","msg":"弱智YouTube <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face